MONGO
INSTALACAO: http://docs.mongodb.org/manual/tutorial/install-mongodb-on-ubuntu/

DRIVER MONGO-PYTHON - PYMONGO:  http://api.mongodb.org/python/current/index.html
INSTALAÇÃO: http://api.mongodb.org/python/current/installation.html

data files: /var/lib/mongo
log files: /var/log/mongo
usuarios devem ser alterados em ambos os arquivos

start: sudo service mongodb start
stop: sudo service mongodb stop
restart: sudo service mongodb restart
